original_font_information.description:
Jaldi is the devanagari version of Asap
wich is based on Ancha (designed by Pablo Cosgaya & Hector Gatti). This family
specially developed for screen and desktop use
offers of a standarised character width on all styles
which helps retain the same length on all text lines.
